   939→            {rendered && (
   940→              <div className="absolute bottom-2 left-2 text-xs text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 pointer-events-none select-none">
   941→                Trascina per spostare • Scroll/pinch per zoom • Click sui nodi per espandere/comprimere
   942→              </div>
